The way people think and act in different places affects how they make deals. We cannot say all people from one country act the same way. For example, it is wrong to say all people from Russia or Japan act in one way. It is better to learn how people's beliefs affect the way they talk about business.

When we meet people from other places, we often think about how they are different from us. To understand people from other places, we need to learn about their history and ideas. We should not try to change how they think or act. This is very important when we want to make deals with them, especially if we need their help more than they need ours. When we go to their country, we should show respect for their ways of doing things.

Different groups have different ways of working, even in the same country. Companies often have their own ways of doing things. Some want workers to stay late, while others let workers go home early. We can see how companies are different in how workers dress, how they talk to each other, and who they choose to hire. Some companies want workers to help poor people, while others only give money to special groups. In America, companies in different cities or areas can be very different from each other.

It is very important to understand what people think is right or wrong. In some places, people think it is very important not to make others look bad. In these places, someone making a deal will not say bad things about their company or their boss. In other places, people think it is good to push hard to get what they want. Before making deals, we should think about these differences. But it is also good to learn about the person we are dealing with as an individual.

In the Bible, it is written that only a foolish person says there is no God. Two important religious thinkers, Anselm and Thomas Aquinas, wrote about why they believe God exists. Both men tried to prove that the God of the Bible is real. To compare their ideas fairly, we must look at how each man explained his belief in the same God. While both made good points, neither gave a complete reason for believing in God.

Let us first look at what Anselm said. He believed that understanding God comes through faith. He said that because we can think about God in our minds, God must be real. He thought we could find proof of God by looking inside ourselves. Anselm said we do not need outside proof to know God exists. We only need to think about what we already know in our hearts. This way of believing without seeing clear proof is called faith.

Thomas Aquinas had different ideas. He said we can prove God exists by using careful thinking and looking at the world around us. He thought we do not need faith to believe in God. This would help spread Christianity because people would not have to believe without proof. They could understand God through clear thinking alone. Aquinas gave five different reasons to show why God must exist. These reasons were about change, causes, why things exist, levels of goodness, and the order in nature. He showed that we can know God exists by seeing how the world works. It is like having a puzzle with one piece missing - you can know what the missing piece looks like by seeing the empty space and the pieces around it.

Writers often try to make readers feel certain ways about important things in their stories. F. Scott Fitzgerald does this in his book The Great Gatsby. He uses special ways of writing to create these feelings. One way he does this is by using colors to mean special things.

In the book, Fitzgerald makes colors like white, gray, red, and pink have special meanings. When he uses these colors later, readers remember the feelings they are supposed to have. This is very clear with how he uses white and gray colors.

White and gray in the book often show things that are all the same, with white meaning rich and clean, while gray means old and tired. We see this from the start. The two women, Daisy and Jordan, always wear white clothes. In fact, many people wear white: Nick wears white pants to Gatsby's party, Tom has on a white shirt when he sees Myrtle, and Catherine's face is white with powder.

Fitzgerald also uses these colors to show regular, common things. Nick goes to work through the white streets of New York. The names of people at Gatsby's parties become gray words in Nick's notes. Many plain buildings and people are described as white or gray. In the poor area called the Valley of Ashes, everything is gray - the cars, the land, and even the people.

After making readers understand what these colors mean, Fitzgerald uses them to tell us something about Daisy. When she appears in white clothes and drives a white car, we start to see her differently. She becomes less special and more like everything else - just something Gatsby wants to have. This helps readers understand that maybe Daisy is not as special as Gatsby thinks she is.

San Diego County grows many foods because the weather is warm and sunny. Farmers grow tomatoes, oranges, green vegetables, and many other foods. They also get honey from bees and milk from cows. Many people want to buy food grown without chemicals, and they often must wait to get it. Some farms let people visit to see how food grows. People can also walk on these farms to see birds and enjoy nature.

These farms can get help from the government while making the land better for wild animals. They can also make money by teaching people about farming. When farmers grow food without chemicals, more kinds of plants and animals can live on the farm. But farming without chemicals is harder work. Farmers must pull out bad plants by hand and find natural ways to stop insects from eating the food. They also need to feed the soil naturally. Small farms often lose more food to problems than big farms do. Making the land good for wild animals takes more work too. Farmers must plant special plants and move their animals around the land carefully. Because this work is hard, farmers often need help with money and knowledge.

The land we are talking about is near a town called Potrero in San Diego County. It is 160 acres of wild land next to a big forest. Many special animals live in this area. Some of these animals are in danger of dying out, like certain rats, frogs, butterflies, and birds. 

Native American people lived on this land for many years. Later, in the late 1800s, people came to raise cows and cut wood. Someone got this land from the government long ago and probably used it for cows or wood since then.

I found this land for sale and looked up ways the government could help a small farmer. I also found another farm nearby that grows food without chemicals to use as an example.

Brothers share a special connection that cannot be broken. This connection brings many feelings like love, pride, anger, and sometimes even mean thoughts. Brothers know each other better than anyone else can. When they look at each other, it is like looking in a mirror. When times are very hard, this connection shows its true nature, whether good or bad. These feelings can lead to serious results.

In the story "The Scarlet Ibis," two brothers show us what this means. The older brother tells the story about his younger brother, Doodle. The story takes place in a beautiful green area where the two boys try to do something that cannot succeed. The older brother feels both very proud and very sad at different times, and in the end, only one brother lives.

The older brother's actions come from his pride. When Doodle was born, the older brother wanted someone to play with and teach things to. He wanted a brother who could run, jump, and climb trees with him. He wanted someone to race with to the water and sit with him high in the pine tree behind their family's barn. But Doodle was born very sick, with a weak heart. The doctors said he might die, and if he lived, he would never be able to run or play hard games.

This made the older brother very sad and angry. He was so upset that he even thought about hurting baby Doodle. But when Doodle smiled at him one day, the older brother's anger went away. This small act gave him hope. It shows that deep down, he truly loved his little brother, even if he sometimes did not act like it.

The human brain is an amazing system that processes information in complex ways. Over time, as humans developed new tools, they found new ways to describe how the brain works. People first thought it was like a writing tablet, then like paper, then like a book, and now like a computer. But we must remember that these simple comparisons can sometimes lead us to wrong ideas about the brain.

The brain first gets information from our senses. These senses change things we feel, hear, and see into signals the brain can use. The brain then changes these signals in different ways. For example, when you look at a black box on a white background, your brain first sees simple things like color and shape. Then, your brain uses what it already knows to help you understand that you are seeing a box more quickly.

The brain also decides what information is important. While your brain sees everything around you, it helps you pay attention only to what matters. For instance, you might not notice every small thing on the ground when you walk, but you might hear someone say your name even in a loud room.

The brain must store information to use it. There are different kinds of memory. Some memories last only seconds, while others can last for years. When you learn something new, your brain first changes it into a form it can save. For words, your brain might remember how they look, sound, or what they mean. Short-term memories may stay active through signals moving between brain cells. Long-term memories are kept through changes in special proteins.

Scientists have different ideas about how the brain organizes what we know. One idea suggests that the brain connects related things together, like linking the word "chair" to "table" because they are both furniture. These connections help us remember and understand things better.

In 2007, the United States faced a serious money problem. Many people lost their jobs. House prices fell sharply. Many big companies failed. These problems continue today, so we must ask: why did this happen, and how can we prevent it?

The crisis began because banks gave home loans to people who could not pay them back. The government helped two big companies, Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac, to buy these bad loans from banks. When people could not pay their loans, the banks lost money. This affected the whole country's money system.

The story starts in 1999 when Bill Clinton was president. He wanted to win more support from voters. His government made it easier for banks to give loans. In 1999, a New York Times writer named Steven Holmes wrote about Fannie Mae. He said the government was pushing the company to give more loans to people with low and middle incomes. Holmes warned this could cause problems if the economy became weak.

Several things made the problem worse. Banks created new types of home loans that were hard to understand. They also sold these loans to other companies. This meant that when house prices fell, it hurt many parts of the economy, not just the housing market.

When house prices finally fell, many banks that had bought these loans lost a lot of money. The five biggest U.S. investment banks owed $4.1 trillion in 2007. Two of these banks were sold for very low prices. One bank closed completely. The other two had to change how they operated. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac owed $5 trillion and needed government help to survive.

Let's talk about telling stories. Writers often want to give too much information at once. This can make readers stop reading or feel tired. Even experienced writers sometimes make this mistake.

It is not good to give too much information all at once.

Most writers know they should show things instead of just telling them. But sometimes we still write long parts where nothing happens, or we try to tell too many things at the same time. We might think we need to explain everything about the past before we can tell the real story. Or we might want to tell every small thing about each person in the story. Both are wrong.

Telling too much means explaining things in simple words instead of showing them happen. In movies, this happens when one person tells another person too many facts at once. In books, the writer does this directly to the readers.

Here is an example. Think about a story where a woman meets a man, they get married, and then he dies. This should not be told quickly in just two pages with only a few words from each person. Instead, the writer should show how the man acts and talks to prove his love. The writer should show how the woman's life becomes better because of him. This helps readers care about both people. When the man dies, readers will feel sad with the woman. They will understand her better.

In other words, a simple story needs more details to make it complete.

As a writer, you must add these details carefully. Sometimes you want to hurry and tell everything about a new person in the story. You might want to say they were in the Air Force, now work at night at a gas station, were married two times, have no children, like to fish, want to own the gas station, and what they ate that morning. But this is not the best way to tell a story.

I watched two news shows from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was NBC 4 on the morning of August 13, 2011. The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio who had hurt his wife with a knife. The man's name was Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture from the police. The story was short because it was still happening. They only said he had attacked his wife several times and the police had caught him. I think they used the right amount of time for this story.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers, who was 18 years old. Someone shot him in the Sharon Woods area, and he was badly hurt. The police had not caught anyone yet. Special police teams were looking into what happened. The story seemed very short. I think this might have been because Travis was a black man in a black area. I have seen for many years that when bad things happen to people who are not white, the news does not talk about it much. When something bad happens to white people, the news talks about it a lot more.

They then talked about a bullet hole found in a medical flying machine. They said it was from a small gun. People who help catch criminals are offering money to anyone who can help find who did this.

The weather news was next. They said it would rain later, and it would not be too hot. They kept this part short so people would keep watching.

They also told about someone taking money from a store on Clime Road. They spent a lot of time saying the person who did it was a black man wearing a shirt with a hood. I thought they talked too much about his skin color.

The last story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez who sold bad things from Texas to Ohio. They said he would be in prison for 300 months instead of saying 25 years. They also said he was Hispanic, which did not seem important to the story.

Let me explain what an ETF is and how it works. An ETF (exchange traded fund) is a special kind of investment that follows the value of many different companies or things, like gold. You can buy and sell it easily, just like a company's stock.

When you buy an ETF, you are really buying small parts of many different companies at once. This helps make your investment safer because you are not putting all your money in just one company. ETFs usually cost less money to own than other similar investments.

There are some things to think about before buying ETFs. You must pay a small fee each time you buy or sell them. However, there are many different kinds of ETFs to choose from.

In this study, we looked at an ETF called IHF to see if it was better to buy the ETF or to buy shares of the ten biggest companies in it separately. The ten biggest companies make up about 64% of the ETF's total value.

When we looked at the numbers, we found something interesting. If you bought shares of just these ten companies in the same amounts as they are in the ETF, you could make about 16% more money than by buying the ETF itself. The investment would also be less risky.

To make sure these findings were real and not just by chance, we needed to look at how much the prices of these investments moved up and down over time. We did this by studying the standard deviation of both the ETF and the ten companies.

Looking at the numbers shown in Figure 17, we saw that far fewer people sent in their travel records during the third month. This was disappointing, and we were not sure why it happened. When winter comes to our school in the northeast United States, fewer people ride bikes or walk to work. This could explain part of the drop. December is also when the school term ends, and everyone is busy finishing work and giving grades. People may have simply forgotten to write down how they traveled. Also, December brings holidays and a long break when many students and teachers do not come to school at all. School starts again in late January, which may explain why that month's numbers were low. But this does not tell us why February's numbers were so low. Perhaps any project like this starts with great interest that naturally falls over time. To fight this drop, we created a special week in March to get people excited about sharing rides. This helped increase the number of records sent in that month. One of our biggest problems was keeping people interested, especially during school breaks and holidays.

Another problem we faced is that people like driving their own cars. They enjoy being free to go where they want, when they want. This is a big part of life in our country. So, we needed to give people good reasons to try other ways of getting to school. We gave out many prizes like food tickets for local eating places, coffee shops, and stores. We also gave tickets for back rubs and books. It would have been interesting to see what would happen if we had given bigger prizes, like a new bike or a special car that uses less gas. This might have helped keep people interested. Our prizes stayed the same all through the project. If we had made the prizes better as time went on, more people might have stayed with the project. The small prizes worked well at first, but telling people they could win a bike in December or a special car in January might have kept more people sending in their travel records.

I studied some old films at the Library of Congress. These were special films made by Thomas Edison between 1895 and 1901. There were fifteen films that used special tricks to fool the eye. These tricks were made by careful cutting and joining of film parts.

Most of these films were very simple. They were shot in one room with the camera staying in one place, like watching a stage show. The camera did not move around. It showed the whole scene from far away or middle distance. Each film was usually just one scene.

At the start of the 1900s, a few films began to do things differently. Some used more than one scene put together. But most trick films were like watching a theater show from your seat. The actors moved from left to right across the screen, like they would on a stage. They did not walk toward or away from the camera.

In one film called "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel" (1900), we can see this clearly. The actors come in from the right side and move back and forth. When they leave the picture, the camera stays still.

These films were always shot from far away or middle distance. They never showed close pictures of faces or things. This was like sitting in a theater, where you see everything happening on the stage at once. The actors stayed away from the camera, so there were no close views.

Most of these early trick films were very short, usually less than one minute. They showed simple magic tricks, like making people appear and disappear. They did not tell long stories. Even though these films looked like one continuous scene to people watching, they were actually made of several pieces of film joined together. For example, in "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots" (1895), if you look carefully, you can see where they cut the film to make it look like her head was cut off.

The Gothic Novel is both old and new at the same time. Some people have said these books are too simple, while others praise them for creating feelings of fear and wonder. The first Gothic Novel was "The Castle of Otranto" by Horace Walpole. He mixed old story-telling methods with new ways of writing to create something different. 

Gothic stories use many ideas from the middle ages, including old buildings and customs. When "The Castle of Otranto" was first written, the word "gothic" was used to describe many different things from the past. Many people thought gothic things were old-fashioned compared to new ideas. But the Gothic Novel was special because it mixed old dramatic stories with new ways of showing how characters think and feel. This is why Gothic stories are still interesting to readers today.

One of the most important ideas in Gothic novels is the code of honor called chivalry. This idea comes from the middle ages, when knights had to follow strict rules about being brave and good. Writers like Walpole used these old ideas because they thought their own time needed more honor and goodness. When Walpole wrote his book, his country was having political problems. He may have thought that people in his time were not as good or moral as people in the past.

We can see this in his book through characters like Frederic. Before we meet him, we learn that he is a prince who has faced many hard times. He shows the qualities of an honorable knight, though Walpole makes these qualities very strong to make a point about what society was missing.

Moving goods from start to finish is called supply chain management. This process begins when a customer orders something and ends when they receive it. Keith Oliver, who helped businesses work better, first used this term in 1982. He explained how to plan and control the movement of goods to make customers happy quickly and well.

There are six main parts in moving goods: making things, getting materials, keeping goods ready, choosing where to work, moving goods around, and sharing information. Business leaders use these six parts to serve customers well.

Making things is the first and most important part. Leaders must know what to make, how much to make, and where to make it. They look at what people want to buy in stores. This helps them decide what customers need. Then they pick the best places to make these things, thinking about how many they can make and how good they will be.

After choosing where to make things, leaders plan when workers will work and how to keep machines running well. Every small part of making things must be planned carefully. If not, it can waste time and money. For example, stores like Walmart and Target have clear plans for everything. They even have rules about what workers should wear and how trucks should bring goods to stores.

The second main part is getting materials. Leaders must decide what each workplace can do best. Sometimes, one thing is made in many different places. Each place has different machines, workers, and special skills. Leaders choose which place should do each part of the work. Sometimes, they ask other companies to help make things. They do this to work faster and keep costs low while still making good things.

Books from the time of Queen Victoria often told stories about rich people and included many small details. Two books from this time, "Oliver Twist" and "Wuthering Heights," were different. These stories used mystery and strange events to help readers better understand the people in the stories and why they acted as they did.

In "Oliver Twist," we see this through Oliver's dreams and times when he is not fully awake. In one part of the story, Oliver is shot and hurt. While he is trying to find help, his mind mixes what is real with what is not real. He thinks he hears two bad men, Sikes and Crackit, talking. He hears guns being fired and people shouting. Lights flash before his eyes. Someone pulls him away, but he does not know who. Through all of this, he feels pain that will not stop.

This part of the story shows us how little control Oliver has over his life. He cannot even try to help himself when he is in danger. It seems that the bad man Fagin has started to break Oliver's spirit. In normal times, anyone would try to save their own life, but Oliver does not even try.

Time itself seems strange to Oliver. The day passes quickly, as if there is no day at all. The night feels both very long because it is so quiet, and very short because the hours move fast.

Two years ago, I helped young students after school with their studies. I was good at teaching English and reading. A teacher asked me to help a young boy named Adrian. He was about nine years old and had trouble reading. I noticed something strange about how he read. He could say some letters well, but others gave him much trouble. Adrian spoke English very well, and I knew he came from a Latin American family.

One day, I met Adrian's mother when I was watching some students. She could not speak English, only Spanish. I knew a little Spanish, so we could talk. Then I understood the problem: Adrian could read, but he did not know the English letters well. I hope he reads better now.

I tell this story to show how language problems affect our schools, especially in California. Sometimes these problems are hard to see. Even when children speak English well, reading can be very hard. We know this problem exists, so what should we do? For Adrian, the answer was simple: he needed help learning English letters and their sounds. But for children who do not speak much English, the answer is not simple. We need many ways to help. Teaching in two languages, putting students in English-speaking classes, having special teachers, and English learning classes are all good ideas. But we need to use all of these ways together.

Teaching in two languages is very good for all students, not just Spanish-speaking ones. Studies show that children who learn in two languages do better in school than others. Some people think this is a waste, but they are wrong. If we used this way of teaching in all classes, every student would learn better. We do not need all teachers to speak two languages. That would be too hard. But we can have special helpers who speak both languages.

Many people learn from a young age that there is something greater than themselves in the world. Some learn about this at church, while others go to different places of worship, or look inside themselves for answers. Many accept the religious beliefs their parents teach them. Others completely reject these ideas, believing only in what they can see and know. People may follow one set of beliefs, then change to follow another. Whatever way we choose, we all try to understand life's big questions in our own way. We look for something to help guide us through dark times.

"A red bird," my father told me when I asked which bird he liked best. We sat on our front porch, hearing rain hit the metal roof as we smoked. Water poured from the roof's edge, falling on the plants below. He looked out at the rain, seeming both thoughtful and far away. He had become much thinner, and his clothes were too big now. His hair was thinner too. He kept looking at the rain, not at me. I felt very alone and scared. I could not tell him how much I would miss him because talking about it would make everything feel too real. I gave him a hug, then moved my chair closer to his. Together, we watched the rain fall in the growing dark.

My father died that December, shortly after I turned twenty-two. The doctors tried to help him with strong medicine, but it only made him live longer in pain. I could not understand why. I asked myself why this would happen if there was a God. At night, I stopped praying. I thought that if God was real, he no longer heard me.

I did not want to watch my father die, so I stayed away. I wanted to remember him as he lived, not as he died. I knew my father better than anyone, and I knew he would not want me to watch him die. I stayed in my bed for three days, waiting to hear news.

No one called to tell me when he died.

John Taylor was an early supporter of the Republican way of thinking in America. He was mainly a farmer, and this work, along with his short time in government, made him known for speaking strongly about personal freedom and government power. His love of farming shaped most of his ideas about how government should work. He tried to protect and support farming, which he thought was the best job, and this affected his views on state power, the Constitution, and the courts.

Taylor thought the United States had a special chance to make a perfect system. This was because the new country did not have old rules that would get in the way of making a government run by the people. He believed strongly that people have natural rights, and that these rights work together. If you take away one right, you harm all the others. He said the government should not be able to touch these rights. In nature, he said, strong and clever but bad people would win, but in a proper society, this should not happen.

To make this good society, Taylor thought we needed a government that understands both the good and bad in people. He was very clear about right and wrong. He said that since people run government, government shows both good and bad human qualities. He thought good rules were those that protect what people own, help farming grow, and stop big business from having too much power. He believed that even if bad people ran the government, good rules would make it work fairly. Taylor thought people always act for their own good, but this only becomes bad when people take from others instead of helping everyone.

Taylor, like other Republicans then, wanted people to follow the Constitution exactly as written. He wanted a small federal government that could only do what the Constitution clearly said it could do. He knew that a big federal government would cost too much money and might become too powerful. But he also thought that just reading the Constitution's words was not enough - people needed to understand what the writers meant. He thought the Declaration of Independence was even more important than the Constitution because it showed that the states should be free to rule themselves.

I looked down at what was in front of me. My mind saw everything but felt nothing. Thoughts came and went quickly. It felt like I wasn't really thinking, just seeing.

Once, an artist told me to buy a book called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." I wanted to learn to draw since I was young. The book teaches many things about art. One lesson is to put a frame around what you want to draw. This makes a complex picture simpler. For example, a bowl of fruit in a kitchen becomes just a bowl of fruit.

At that moment, looking down at the bowl, I couldn't think about art frames. I could only stand and look. Famous artists like Picasso used blue colors, Monet liked green, and old Italian artists used many colors. If I were an artist, this would be my brown picture, my brown story.

My fingers touched the tool I needed. My hand moved through the air as my mind told it what to do. The water moved smoothly and clearly. Small pieces broke away and disappeared. Moving more quickly the second time, my hand pushed the toilet handle again. The brown mess stayed at the bottom of the toilet, not moving.

I stood there holding a mop, wearing a green tie that felt tight around my neck. I was not happy about what someone had left in the bathroom at the store where I worked. After trying to flush several times, I pulled some toilet paper from the wall. I wrapped my hand in paper until it looked like a cooking glove. Then, like someone reaching into an oven for food, I had to reach into the toilet bowl...

Young people are dying while driving cars. Several things make driving dangerous for the youngest drivers in America. The National Institutes of Health says that young people's brains are not ready for the dangers of driving. Not having enough practice is also a big problem. This lack of experience leads to more deadly crashes, cars turning over, driving too fast, and going off the road.

Young drivers have more problems when they drive with friends their age, which they often do. A study by researchers in Southern California showed that having young passengers in the car makes crashes more likely.

Some states try to make young drivers safer by giving them special licenses. These licenses say when they can drive and do not let them carry other young people in their cars.

But these special licenses are only a temporary fix. The real problem is that the youngest drivers cannot handle the dangers of driving safely. One expert who studies how people think believes even age 18 is too young to drive. He found that people under age 20 often do dangerous things just for fun. It makes sense to wait until people are older to let them drive.

If we keep giving driver's licenses to young people, more will die on the roads. In the coming years, many more young people will be old enough to drive, which could make the problem worse.

There is a simple way to fix this. Schools could still teach driving, but no one under 18 could drive a car. New drivers would still need to practice with an adult and learn the rules. Because young drivers have problems in all states, one law for the whole country would help keep young people safe everywhere.

This idea is not new, but it could save many lives.

This paper looks at three parts of Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). First, it explains what the disorder is. Then, it shows how doctors find it in patients. Finally, it tells how teachers can help students with CAPD in regular classrooms.

CAPD is a brain problem that makes it hard for people to understand what they hear. People with CAPD can hear sounds normally. However, their brains cannot process these sounds correctly. For example, they may have trouble understanding words when there is other noise nearby, or they may find it hard to tell where sounds are coming from.

Doctors first noticed this problem in the 1950s. They saw it in children who had trouble talking and understanding others. Since then, many doctors have studied CAPD and created tests to find it in patients.

People with CAPD may have several problems. They might not know where sounds come from. They might find it hard to tell different sounds apart. They might not understand changes in how people speak, like when someone is joking. They might also have trouble remembering the order of sounds they hear.

To find out if someone has CAPD, doctors watch how the person listens and responds to different sounds. They may ask questions about how well the person understands speech in different situations. They might also give special listening tests. There is no single test that can show for sure if someone has CAPD. Also, doctors do not know what causes this problem. The tests often involve asking people to listen to different words or numbers at the same time and then repeat what they heard.

I want to study to become a social worker. My goal is to work for the government helping children who have been hurt by their families. I want to help families who are having problems. I believe I can bring important things to this work: helping others, showing respect, doing what is right, and always learning to do better at my job. These things are important not just for work, but also to me as a person.

I have always wanted to help people, but I was not sure what kind of work to do. In school, I saw many young people run away from their problems. Some dealt with their troubles in ways that were not good. This made me want to study how people think and act. After finishing school in 2009, I took some time to think about my future. 

That summer, I met a young boy at my friend's house. He was there because his parents were hurting him. The next day, he called the police about his parents. I went to help and told the police about my education in studying how people think. They asked me to talk to the parents because they could not do anything to help the boy. The parents seemed worried and said their son was just causing trouble. After this, I knew I wanted to be a social worker to help children with family problems.

I also believe everyone should be treated fairly. Our society says each person is important, but often pushes people to be the same as others. I do not like being told I must be like everyone else. In school, I showed this by looking different from others and standing up for people who were treated badly because they were different. I joined groups that helped people who were treated unfairly. I will keep working to make sure everyone is treated fairly.

This paper looks at two ways to understand sleep problems, especially when people cannot sleep well. One way looks at how the body works and what we get from our parents. The other way looks at how where we live, our culture, and our money affect our sleep.

Sleep problems can be grouped in different ways. Some start on their own, while others happen because of mental health issues or other health problems. The most common sleep problem is when people cannot fall asleep or stay asleep. This is called insomnia. Some people have the opposite problem - they sleep too much. Others might walk in their sleep or have bad dreams.

Scientists found that special cells in the brain help control when we are awake or asleep. They did tests with mice to learn how these brain cells work. They found that certain parts of brain cells, called receptors, are very important for sleep. When these receptors work well, animals can sleep normally. When they do not work well, sleep becomes hard.

This information helps us understand why some people have trouble sleeping. If someone's parents had sleep problems, they might get the same problems. This can make life hard because people need good sleep to do well at school or work. When people cannot sleep well, it affects many parts of their daily life.

I have been a student at this university for more than two years now. Moving around our large school area is often hard for many students, including me. When I first came here, I lived in a room far on the east side of school. Walking from my room to my classes near the middle of school could take 25 minutes, especially when the weather was bad. 

An older student told me that years ago, the east living areas were far from other buildings, with much empty land between them. Now that empty space has new sports fields and big buildings. As our school grows bigger, it becomes harder to get from place to place. The best answer to this problem is the bicycle. However, just having bicycles is not enough. Students need to use them, and the school needs to make it easier for bicycle riders.

I talked to a friend who just started riding his bicycle again after stopping for many years. He said he did not know why he ever stopped. "Bicycles are wonderful," he said. "For some time, people thought bicycles were not good to use, but they are the best way to move around." Riding a bicycle is good for your health and uses very little energy. A simple meal can give you enough power to ride very far.

I now live away from the school area, but my home is as far from classes as some school rooms are. Getting a bicycle was the best thing I did this year. Every day, I have class in a building that would take 25 minutes to reach by walking. On my bicycle, I can get there in 5 minutes if I ride fast. The only problem is that the most direct road is often hard to use, whether walking or riding. 

Walking is fine, but I do not have enough time. Without my bicycle, I would have to walk everywhere. Walking to just one of my classes would take 40 more minutes each day. That means more than two hours every week just for one class. When you think about going to other classes and meetings, it takes too much time.

In his book "Brave New World," Aldous Huxley warns us about the dangers of technology and business control. He creates a future world where people are taught to value the group more than themselves. They learn from birth to only care about being happy right now.

The people in this world are like pieces in a game, controlled by powerful leaders. They can only think in ways that these leaders allow. Huxley shows how big businesses and their systems can harm society. The story points out problems he saw growing in the economy of his time.

In the book, regular people do not understand how money and power really work. They only think about what they can get for themselves. The lower classes in the story, called Delta and Gamma, cannot think freely. While they sleep, they hear messages that make them want to buy things and spend money. The top leader uses this to control them. The lower classes do not know they are being controlled, and they believe in a system that keeps them down. Even most of the upper classes, called Alpha and Beta, accept things as they are.

People in this future world do not form real friendships or relationships. Even the main characters seem empty, without much personality. This might show how Huxley thought technology and business control could take away people's ability to think and feel freely. There is no love in this world. Men only talk about how women look, and women speak without shame about their physical relationships. Each group accepts their place in society without question. They obey and keep buying things, believing this makes them better, just as their leaders want them to think.

Four years ago, I studied Islam at my local college. In class, we often talked about whether Islam was a religion that promoted peace or conflict. This question seems even more important today. Since the attacks of September 11, 2001, I have seen how news reports about Islam have changed. At first, many news stories were negative. Now, they show much more acceptance of Islam in America. In 2001, it would have been hard to imagine having a presidential candidate like Barack Obama, who has family ties to Islam.

The life story of Muhammad interests me because what I read seems different from what I learned before. I used to think Muhammad made people join his religion by force when he took control of their lands. However, the book shows him as a good man who was not understood by others. It says people came to him freely when they saw the truth in his words.

I notice that some stories about Muhammad are very similar to stories about Jesus. For example, there is a story where Muhammad made a small amount of food become enough to feed forty men. This reminds me of Jesus feeding many people. I think the writers wanted to make Muhammad seem like a humble teacher who did special things. This bothers me because it seems to copy the special acts of Jesus.

The book has many stories about people becoming Muslims. But these stories often come from someone who heard it from someone else, who heard it from another person. This makes me doubt if the stories are true.

What troubles me most is how the book tries to show Muhammad as a good, quiet, and wise man. This does not match with other things I have learned about how Muhammad gained power. I wonder if Muslims today know the full story of their religion's beginning.

The ideas Jesus taught during his life were quickly changed as Christian thinking grew after his death. Looking at history, we can see Christianity moving further from what Jesus first taught. Today, more people seem to understand this and want change. While some people want to keep old ways of thinking, they may be too few to stop change.

In the years ahead, Christians will learn more about their history. They will want to know what ideas were added to their religion after Jesus, and what Jesus really meant to teach. This change may take many years, but it will happen. Christians will slowly remove added ideas until only Jesus' original teaching about God remains.

When this happens in America and Europe, many people will try to follow only what Jesus taught. Churches will still be important, but they will lead people back to simpler beliefs. Instead of many different Christian groups with different ideas, more people will share the same beliefs.

History shows us that big changes can happen. For example, Rome first tried to destroy Christians, but later became Christian itself. America moved from having slaves to having African-American leaders. The coming change in Christianity will be like this. People will look for Jesus' original message, and many different Christian groups will become more alike. To understand Jesus better, people will learn to read his words as having deeper meaning, not just their simple meaning.

Looking back in history, we find Judaism came before Christianity. By the time Rome took control of Jerusalem in 63 BCE, Jewish people believed in one God, followed their holy books, and thought God had given them their religion. But Jewish people were divided into different groups: the Sadducees, Pharisees, Essenes, Zealots, and common people.

I think "The Jungle" shows that people are naturally wanting things only for themselves. They care about making their own lives better but do not help others who have less. The book shows this in many ways, especially through the factory owners and managers.

These business leaders only want to make their companies bigger and richer. They do not care who gets hurt as they try to grow. In the book, Upton Sinclair describes how the factory buildings stand dark against the sky, with smoke coming from tall chimneys. This smoke spreads far into the distance. He wants us to see how the factories hurt the air and land around them. The owners do not worry about the people or animals their factories harm. They ignore the dirty smoke from their buildings and the animal waste that runs from the many animal holding areas.

The owners also do not care about the workers who make them rich. They will do anything to save or make more money. Workers might lose their jobs without warning, and the companies do not help them find new work. During this time, there were few laws to protect workers. This meant owners could make people work long hours in dangerous places. The workers had to accept these bad conditions both at work and in their homes. There was no one to help them or give them information about their rights.

While there were some worker groups called unions, these often took advantage of the poor workers instead of helping them. The workers could not escape their hard lives. Many of them came from other countries and were very poor. They had to depend on cruel business owners who treated them like slaves. In these terrible conditions, people often became hopeless and desperate.

Edgar Allan Poe wrote a poem called "Dream-Land" which he thought was one of his better works. In this poem, Poe uses the word "Thule" two times. This word comes from old stories about a far-away island north of Britain. While the word appeared in very old writing, Poe likely got it from more recent German writing.

Poe read many German writers. One of these writers was named Goethe, who wrote a famous story called "Faust." Inside "Faust" was a shorter poem about "The King of Thule." This poem tells of a king whose wife dies after giving him a special cup. The king becomes very sad, drinks too much, and finally walks to a high place where he throws the cup into the sea and dies.

The king in Goethe's poem and the person in Poe's "Dream-Land" are very much alike. Both are very sad and alone. This might show how Poe felt about his own problems with drinking. Poe used the word "Thule" in another story called "The Pit and the Pendulum" around the same time.

When we read "Dream-Land," we see a dark, lonely place where the speaker sees dead friends and a world without bright colors. This is very much like the sad world of the King of Thule. It seems Poe may have been writing about the same kind of feelings that Goethe wrote about in his poem.

Poe knew about Goethe's writing because Goethe was very famous at that time. Many people were making new versions of Goethe's works, so Poe would have had many chances to read them. Also, other writers Poe respected, like Tennyson, spoke highly of Goethe's work.

Can a store be forced to pay extra money as punishment in California if a customer gets hurt from falling on spilled food when the store manager knew about the danger but did nothing?

Here are the important facts: A woman named Jennifer Palmer fell in a grocery store and hurt her back badly. The fall happened because there was applesauce on the floor. Two workers had told the store manager about the spilled applesauce earlier. The manager, Paul Martin, did not clean it up because he was eating his dinner. Five other people had fallen in the same store that year.

The law in California says stores must pay extra money as punishment if they do very bad things that hurt people. The store must know that what they are doing could hurt someone, and they must choose not to fix the problem anyway.

In this case, the manager knew about the spill for thirty minutes before Ms. Palmer fell. He also knew that other people had fallen in his store before. He still chose not to clean up the spill or ask someone else to do it. Because he knew about the danger but did nothing, a judge will probably let Ms. Palmer ask for extra money as punishment.

The store might have to pay both for Ms. Palmer's medical care and extra money to teach them to be more careful in the future. This is because the manager's choice to ignore the spill was very wrong, especially since he knew it could hurt someone.

She always felt she needed something. This feeling would not go away. It began when she was 14, as she entered her teenage years. Now at 17, the feeling remained. She knew she wanted a person, not a thing. Yet no boys interested her. Some boys liked her and tried to get her attention, but she felt nothing for them. She often wondered why she was different from other teenage girls. After thinking about this for years, she had ideas but no clear answers. So she continued to live, always wondering about her feelings.

Life at home was usually quiet. Her parents were good people who lived peacefully. They rarely fought with each other or with her. The only problems came when she tried to show she could make her own choices. Her parents were calm, but she was full of life and fun. People liked her because she was both friendly and kind.

But this day was not quiet. As she walked through the house looking for something to do, she heard her mother cry out from the kitchen. She ran to the kitchen asking, "Mom? Mom, what is wrong?" Her mother was on the floor, clearly hurting. She kept saying "ow" over and over. The daughter went to her mother to help. "Please... take me to the hospital," her mother said with difficulty. "Show me how to lift you," the daughter said. She was glad she had learned how to lift heavy things. She carried her mother to the car, put her in the back seat, and drove away.

The hospital always smells clean but scary. The daughter did not notice this because she could only think about her mother. She carried her mother in quickly and called for help. doctors came quickly. They put her mother on a bed with wheels and took her away to check her. The daughter had to wait and worry.

Her mother had fallen while trying to reach something high up in the kitchen.

This study looked at how eating a Mediterranean-style diet affects heart health. The diet includes lots of plants, nuts, whole grains, fish, and healthy oils. It limits foods from animals. A small amount of wine is allowed.

Earlier studies showed that people who follow this diet have better heart health and live longer. One study found that this diet works better than a low-fat diet for losing weight and improving blood test results in heavy people.

The researchers watched 74,886 women for 20 years. These women were nurses between 38 and 63 years old. When the study began, none had heart problems or diabetes. Six times during the study, the women told researchers what they ate by filling out food forms. Almost all the women stayed in the study for the full 20 years.

The researchers checked hospital records and death records to confirm when women had heart attacks or strokes. They also looked at other things that affect health, like exercise, smoking, and medicine use.

To understand eating patterns better, they averaged what each woman ate over time. They also considered other things that could affect the results, like age and exercise.

After studying the numbers carefully, they found that women who followed the Mediterranean diet most closely had fewer heart problems. During the 20 years, 2,391 women had heart attacks, 1,763 had strokes, and 1,077 died from heart disease or stroke. Women who followed the diet best had about 29% less chance of having heart problems compared to those who followed it least.

A young actress stands on a street with a sign. The sign suggests that the spirit of Hitler lives in Burma. 

Burma, also called Myanmar, is a country in Asia. Since 1962, military leaders have controlled the country with force. In 2007, people went into the streets to protest against the government. Many of these protesters were Buddhist religious men wearing orange clothes. People called these protests the "Orange Movement" because of the clothes these men wore.

At first, the government let the protests continue peacefully. Then, things became violent. The military attacked religious buildings and hurt many people. They stopped news writers from other countries from doing their work. They killed a news photographer from Japan who was taking pictures of the protests. The government said thirteen people died. However, a military officer who left his job said thousands of people were killed.

Sadly, this kind of violence has happened many times in history. Governments often try to stop people who speak against them. This happened in China in 1989, when students and workers gathered in a place called Tiananmen Square to protest. Many people died there. In the 1990s, one group in Rwanda killed many people from another group. In the 1930s and 1940s, Hitler killed millions of Jewish people in Europe.

These terrible events show us how some leaders will do anything to keep power. They remind us why we must speak up when we see wrong things happening in the world.

Duke Ellington was one of the greatest jazz musicians in history. He led his band for many years and helped create a special sound in jazz music. While he played the piano, his real skill was in writing music that made each person in his band sound their best.

Ellington knew how to write music that let players make their own special sounds. He also knew how to make all the different instruments work together to create beautiful music. He understood what each player could do best, and he used this knowledge to write some of the most important jazz music ever made.

The Grove Music book talks about how Ellington used the human voice in new ways. In his song "Creole Love Call," he used the voice like another instrument in the band, without any words. This was something new at the time. The song shows how well he could write for different players. It is a slow blues song with six parts:

Part 1: Voice and wind instruments play back and forth
Part 2: Quiet trumpet plays alone
Part 3: High clarinet plays with soft piano
Part 4: Full band plays together
Part 5: Wind instruments lead, with other instruments adding beat
Part 6: Voice and winds play together again, with voice making special sounds

The song ends with a voice run and an unusual sound from the trombone.

In other songs like "Hot and Bothered" and "It Don't Mean a Thing," Ellington continued to use voices and instruments in special ways. He had singers make sounds like instruments, and he had instruments make sounds like voices. This helped create the special sound that made his music famous.

How do living things change over time? What guides these changes? In 1917, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that we could not yet describe living things using math. This is still true today.

Recently, scientists have used math to study how sea shells grow and change over time. Our study looks at a type of sea animal called Prunum. We want to understand how these animals grow their shells and how the shells have changed over many years.

We took X-ray pictures of different Prunum shells. We put the numbers we found into a computer program called CerioShell. This helped us see what kinds of shell shapes are possible for Prunum. We also watched how living Prunum grow to better understand how these animals have changed over a very long time.

A shell is like a tube that goes around in a circle many times. Each circle is called a whorl. The whorls wrap around the middle of the shell, which is called the columella. A line between each whorl is called a suture. The biggest whorl is usually the last one, called the body whorl. All other whorls make up the spire. The top of the spire is called the apex, and the bottom is called the base. The animal comes out through a hole called the aperture.

You can look at shells from different sides: the top, bottom, front, and back. Usually, people look at shells from the front, with the opening facing them and the top pointing up.

To count whorls, look at the shell from the top. Find where the first line between whorls starts. Draw a line to split the shell in two parts. Then count the whorls from this line. You can count parts of whorls in quarters.

As the animal builds its shell, it makes new openings that follow a path through space. Scientists can measure this path by looking at the center of each opening and how wide and tall it is.

We can show this path with pictures and math. Once we understand the math, we can change numbers to see how different shells might grow.

In Indonesia, the number of babies and young children who die has stayed almost the same for the past ten years. The country is doing well in some areas, like providing clean water. However, it is not doing well enough in keeping mothers and children healthy. There are many reasons for this, which suggest the whole health system needs to be made stronger.

More births now happen with trained health workers present - about 72 out of 100 births. However, many of these workers are traditional birth helpers who cannot help if there are serious problems during birth. This means many mothers still die from losing too much blood. Also, fewer sick children under five years old are being seen by doctors. We also know that not enough mothers get care after having their babies.

Special operations to help difficult births (called c-sections) are not common enough - only 4 out of 100 births. In cities, 7 out of 100 births are c-sections, but in rural areas, only 2 out of 100 are. This shows that health care is better in cities than in rural areas. Also, rich people get much more health care than poor people. The difference is very large - 27 out of 100. Poor people often cannot pay for health care.

To make things better, Indonesia must decide how to provide more health services. They can either make special programs just for mothers and babies, or they can make the whole health system stronger. Special programs might work faster and be easier to manage. But these programs can cause problems. When a lot of money goes to one health program, other important health services get less money and fewer workers. Also, having many different programs doing the same work wastes time and money.

Over the past hundred years, popular music has grown to include many different types. There are now so many kinds of music that it is hard to list them all. Each type of music, like rap, rock, country, jazz, and folk, has created many smaller groups within itself.

Heavy metal rock music has become one of the most interesting types of popular music in the past forty years. It shows many different feelings, usually dark ones. Soon after heavy metal began, musicians found they could change it in many ways. They made new kinds of heavy metal music, and this continues today.

Now there are so many different kinds of heavy metal that it is hard to say exactly what it is. It has taken ideas from many other types of music. To understand today's heavy metal music, we must understand how it grew and changed.

Heavy metal is often about dark things. It uses more of everything - more loud sounds, more angry words, and more dramatic shows. Heavy metal musicians must be very good at playing their instruments. In the middle of the 1970s, many musicians used drugs, which led them to make strange music. Heavy metal was different from other popular music because it showed the dark side of life. Some of these dark ideas came from music written hundreds of years ago.

One of the first heavy metal songs might have been "Helter Skelter" by the Beatles. They wrote this song to show they could make music as strong as the Rolling Stones. The song had dark words and a wild sound that went up and down, like the effects of drugs. They put this song on their White Album to prove they could make powerful music.

Many years before artists started making strange dream pictures, Henri Rousseau was already painting his own dreams. His 1910 painting called "The Dream" shows a woman looking with wonder at the land she sees in her sleep. The painting also shows what Rousseau himself wanted in life. From the start, he hoped other artists would accept and praise his work, but this was not easy to achieve. "The Dream" shows how Rousseau had to choose between two paths: either paint like others to be accepted, or follow his own special way of making art.

To understand this painting better, we should know about Rousseau's life. He was born on May 21, 1844, in Laval, France. His father fixed metal items and sold hardware, making enough money to live well. Rousseau never went to art school. Instead, he worked for the city collecting money from people at gates until he was forty years old. People wrongly called him a customs worker. His life was very sad at times. His first wife died, and before that, eight of their babies died. Only one child lived, a daughter named Julia. To feel better, he started painting.

Unlike other artists of his time who painted fancy pictures of poor people, Rousseau painted more simply, like ordinary people did. He wanted very much to be accepted by other artists. This was hard because he started painting late in life and had no training. He worked at the same time as many famous artists like Matisse. While Matisse tried very hard not to paint like everyone else, Rousseau actually wanted to paint pictures that looked like what others were doing, so the art world would accept him.

Many wise people have seen a close link between what is right and what is beautiful. I believe there is a deep reason for this connection. The poet John Keats wrote that beauty and truth are the same thing, and this is all we need to know.

We learn most things in life through school or through what happens to us. But we seem to understand right and wrong, and beauty, in a different way. When we study what makes things right or beautiful, we try to explain why we feel the way we do. We do not make rules about how to create beautiful things or how to be good.

When we talk about art or right actions, we cannot fully explain why they move us. For example, when people discuss why the Mona Lisa is a great painting, they might talk about colors or shapes. But these words do not really tell us why it is special. Often, when someone talks about art they love, they first say, "There is just something about it." I think both art and right actions have something special that cannot be fully described.

The writer Flannery O'Connor said that stories tell us things that cannot be said in any other way. No matter how well we describe a story, there is always something more that we cannot explain. The same is true about right and wrong.

I believe art and right actions are closely connected because we feel them deeply in a way we cannot fully explain. This is especially true with stories and books. Stories are important to us because they show us what matters in life. They help us think about what is right and wrong, just as we must do in our own lives.

Germany today is a strong and united nation. Its culture spreads from the mountains in the south to the northern seas. You can feel this same culture as you travel from the western city of Cologne to the eastern city of Dresden. Germany's special way of life comes from many different groups of people who lived there long ago.

The old name for Germany was Germania. No one knows exactly where this name came from. The Roman writer Tacitus said it came from a group called the Tungrians. Julius Caesar was the first to write the word "Germanus" when he wrote about his wars. He learned this name from people called the Gauls. Some think the name comes from the word for "spear," while others say it means "to shout" in an old language.

Tacitus wrote in the year 98 that the German people were different from others. He thought they had always lived in their land and did not come from somewhere else. He asked why anyone would want to leave warm places like Asia or Africa to live in the cold, wild German lands.

The Romans did not want to live in Germania, but they did trade with the German people. Sometimes Roman armies would go into Germania to get goods or fight. The German people lived near the edge of the Roman Empire. They sold things they made and found in their land. Many German men also worked as soldiers in the Roman army.

In the play Twelfth Night, we see how hiding one's true self can help someone for a time, but can also cause problems. The story shows that people must eventually return to their real selves, or they might lose who they truly are. When someone stops hiding, they might lose friends. So, people must choose between being true to themselves or keeping their relationships with others. Some people may not mind finding out they were fooled, but others might become very angry.

When someone pretends to be the opposite sex, it raises many questions. The main question is why they feel they must hide who they are. In the story, Viola does this to stay safe. She says she needs help to serve a noble man, and must hide her women's clothes.

Viola arrives in a strange place and thinks she must act like a man to protect herself. This works, but it keeps her from making friends with other women. Things get harder when Olivia thinks Viola is really a man named Sebastian and falls in love with her. Also, Viola must deal with her own feelings for Orsino, who thinks she is a man.

Today's readers might see the play differently. It shows how pretending to be someone else can bring hidden feelings into the open. This is true for both Olivia and Orsino. We might wonder if Olivia loves Viola because she looks like a man, or if Olivia might have deeper, hidden feelings for women. But this is probably not what the writer meant. Shakespeare likely wanted to make fun of people who only care about how others look.

We can see this when Olivia quickly changes her love from Viola (who she knows as Cesario) to Sebastian. After this, she starts to think of Viola as family instead of someone to love, calling her "sister."

German control of its colonies was often cruel, especially in South West Africa where many local people were killed. However, the way Germans ruled their colonies was different in each place. This was also true for schools. When the British took control of German East Africa in 1919, they found many African people who could read and write. Other writers also said good things about German schools in places like Kamerun.

The story was very different in South West Africa, which is now called Namibia. In East Africa, the government built schools and helped teach local people. But in South West Africa, they left this work to church groups and gave them little help. The government did spend money on schools for European children there. They built public schools and helped church schools that taught European children. These choices about schools affected South West Africa for many years. While other German colonies had many educated African people, most people in South West Africa could not read or write. This happened because of many different reasons in society, government, and business.

Many people have written about schools in German colonies. Most of these books were written in German during the early 1900s when Germany still controlled these places. These early books just told what the schools were like. Later, books in English looked at how schools were different in each colony. One important writer named Cohen studied schools in South West Africa and East Africa. He found that having many European settlers in South West Africa made its schools very different from other colonies.

South West Africa had better weather than other German colonies, even though much of it was dry desert land. Because of this, more Europeans lived there. By 1913, almost 15,000 white people lived in South West Africa. The next highest number was in East Africa, with only 5,336 European people.

The United States and Mexico were not friendly nations for many years, from 1836 to 1893. The worst time in their relationship was during the Mexican-American War of 1846-1848. In this war, the United States fought Mexico and won. As a result, the United States took control of Texas and the Southwest area.

The two countries had many differences. They did not share the same religion, culture, or ways of life. They also fought over land and other important things. This kind of problem is common between countries that share a border.

The United States has had difficult relationships with few countries in Latin America. Mexico and Cuba are the main examples because they are very close to the United States. Other Latin American countries have usually been friendly with the United States.

Religion was a big problem between the United States and Mexico. In the 1800s, Americans did not like the Catholic religion that was common in Mexico. This dislike came from old problems between England and Spain, the countries that once controlled the United States and Mexico.

During the 57 years of poor relations, the United States and Mexico had 17 different fights. Most of these fights were about problems at the border. Bad people would cross the border to cause trouble in both countries. This continued until both countries put soldiers at the border to stop it.

The problems between the two countries began to get better when Mexico started to depend more on the United States. By the late 1800s, the United States was no longer trying to take Mexican land. Instead, American businesses wanted to work in Mexico. This helped make the two countries more friendly.

Fifteen years ago, I became sick with an illness I did not know about. This made me unable to work or do many normal things.

I was a nurse then. I chose this job because I wanted to feel safe, something I did not have when I was young. People told me, "You will always find work because people will always be sick." Even though I wanted to be a scientist or writer, I became a nurse instead.

Then at age 46, I was alone with very little money and could not work. Today, I still cannot work. After fifteen years of getting help money from the government, I own almost nothing. I live day by day, but it is hard. I feel unsafe and worry much. While nothing is sure anymore, I know one truth: I could not have lived these years without help from my family and friends. When bad things happen, you do not feel strong at all.

Life will always have big and small problems. No one can promise anything, and sometimes problems are too big to fix alone.

I agree that in America, we should not depend only on the government, which is not working well. Instead, Americans should learn to trust and help each other again, rather than try to live alone.

Some people talk about how Americans should be strong alone. But what really helped our early settlers was working together and sharing. The people who went west in wagons did not make it by being alone.

So yes, be ready for problems. I have emergency supplies: medical things, water cleaning tablets, and window covers. I have lights, batteries, matches, and stored food. If you can grow food or have a wood stove, that is good.

But most important: know the people who live near you.

Around 2,500 years ago, a prince was born who would later be known as the Buddha. During his life, he left his wealthy life behind and found deep wisdom. His teachings created Buddhism, and the oldest form is called Theravada Buddhism.

The religion has changed much since Buddha's time. In Sri Lanka, where many follow Theravada Buddhism, people hold a yearly water ceremony. Both religious teachers and common people join this event. While Buddha never spoke about such celebrations, they have become important to the people. These changes can be seen in both small traditions and the deep beliefs of the religion. The Buddhist community has had to change its basic ideas over time because of different forces, both from inside and outside their group.

Let me explain some important words we will use. When we say "inside forces," we mean changes that come from Buddhists themselves. "Outside forces" come from people who are not Buddhist. Some forces try to hurt Buddhism - we call these "harmful." Other forces neither help nor hurt Buddhism on purpose - we call these "neutral," though they might still affect the religion.

The main ideas of Buddhism are important to understand. Buddhists believe in three special things: the Buddha (their teacher), the Dhamma (their holy books), and the Sangha (their religious community). Their holy books are split into three parts. One part has Buddha's teachings, another has rules for living, and the third part talks about deep ideas about life.

These deep ideas include beliefs that there is no eternal soul, that life includes suffering, and that nothing lasts forever. Buddhists believe people are born again and again until they understand these truths. When someone fully understands, they stop wanting things too much, stop hating, and stop being confused about life.

The religion has rules for living. Regular people follow five main rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not act badly in relationships, and do not use drugs or alcohol. Religious teachers must follow many more rules. The most important teaching is that life includes suffering, that wanting things causes suffering, and that people can learn to end their suffering.
